; 4198 : 	// 2) Small Transmitter/receiver drift during the frame by averaging and adjusting to constellation to the average. 
; 4199 : 	//   It only processes phase values close to the nominal to avoid generating too large of a correction from outliers: +/- 30 deg for 4PSK, +/- 15 deg for 8PSK
; 4200 : 	//  Is very affective in handling initial tuning error.  
